memberdef.name: ENQUEUE_INFO
memberdef.initializer: do { \ OSModuleInfo* __prev; \ \ __prev = (queue)->tail; \ if (__prev == NULL) \ (queue)->head = (info); \ else \ __prev->link.next = (info); \ (info)->link.prev = __prev; \ (info)->link.next = NULL; \ (queue)->tail = (info); \ } \ while (0)

memberdef.name: DEQUEUE_INFO
memberdef.initializer: do { \ OSModuleInfo* __next; \ OSModuleInfo* __prev; \ \ __next = (info)->link.next; \ __prev = (info)->link.prev; \ \ if (__next == NULL) \ (queue)->tail = __prev; \ else \ __next->link.prev = __prev; \ \ if (__prev == NULL) \ (queue)->head = __next; \ else \ __prev->link.next = __next; \ } \ while (0)
